data.name: Genta, Gateman of Dark World
data.desc: You can discard this card to the GY; add 1 "The Gates of Dark World" from your Deck to your hand. If this card is banished, and you control a "Dark World" card: You can Special Summon this card. You can only Special Summon "Genta, Gatekeeper of Dark World(s)" once per turn.
